275
00:14:06.243 --> 00:14:09.743
It just so happens to be the day this shop is closed.

276
00:14:09.743 --> 00:14:13.643
You said that the man who works here lives near Beika Park, right?

277
00:14:13.643 --> 00:14:15.243
