370
00:19:16.752 --> 00:19:19.652
Don't move!

371
00:19:19.652 --> 00:19:21.652
Stand right there!

372
00:19:22.952 --> 00:19:25.652
Stop! You thief!

373
00:19:25.652 --> 00:19:27.152
Thief?

374
00:19:27.152 --> 00:19:28.952
Stop!

375
00:19:28.952 --> 00:19:30.152
Get out of my way!

376
00:19:47.052 --> 00:19:49.152
I would like to question you regarding the series of thefts

377
00:19:49.152 --> 00:19:52.152
