378
00:19:53.952 --> 00:19:55.252
Okay.

379
00:19:55.252 --> 00:19:56.652
Officer Arai, can you take care of him for me.

380
00:19:56.652 --> 00:19:57.852
Yes, sir.

381
00:20:00.852 --> 00:20:04.352
You're Mr. Tetsuji Odawara?

382
00:20:08.452 --> 00:20:10.352
Yes.

383
00:20:14.352 --> 00:20:16.452
Yasuyo.

384
00:20:19.952 --> 00:20:23.552
Who on earth are you?

385
00:20:25.952 --> 00:20:27.952
Ms. Akimoto, he is...

386
00:20:27.952 --> 00:20:29.552
In order to protect

387
00:20:29.552 --> 00:20:32.352
a woman going home late at night,

388
00:20:32.352 --> 00:20:35.852
in order to see that she gets safely home,

389
00:20:35.852 --> 00:20:37.652
