390
00:20:37.652 --> 00:20:39.352
How did you know that?

391
00:20:39.352 --> 00:20:40.952
What are you talking about?

392
00:20:40.952 --> 00:20:43.652
But, you know, sir, a person whos not a police officer

393
00:20:43.652 --> 00:20:47.252
