397
00:20:57.852 --> 00:21:01.552
You did it the wrong way.

398
00:21:13.452 --> 00:21:14.652
Yasuyo.

399
00:21:14.652 --> 00:21:17.852
I'm arresting you for faking identity

400
00:21:17.852 --> 00:21:19.652
