401
00:21:19.652 --> 00:21:21.652
Shall we go then?

402
00:21:26.952 --> 00:21:28.952
Wait.

403
00:21:32.252 --> 00:21:36.052
I'll go to eat ramen again.

404
00:23:14.952 --> 00:23:18.552
"Tetsuryu"

